<sect1>Inline Markup<p>

<p>
Normal text. <bf>Bold text</bf>. <em>Italic text</em>. <bf><em>Underline text</em></bf>.
Strikethrough. <tt>Monospaced text</tt>.

<p>
<bf>Bold and <em>italic</em> combined</bf>. <em>Italic and <bf><em>underline</em></bf> combined</em>.

<p>
Escaped char: \<bf>not bold</bf>.

