cell 4<colsep>cell 5<colsep>cell 6
</tabular></table>

<sect2>Aligned Table<p>

<table><tabular ca="lll">
Name<colsep>Age<colsep>City<rowsep>
Alice<colsep>30<colsep>Paris<rowsep>
Bob<colsep>25<colsep>Lyon<rowsep>
Charlotte<colsep>35<colsep>Marseille
</tabular></table>

<sect1>Special Characters<p>

<p>
Angle brackets: &lt; and &gt;
Ampersand: &amp;
At sign: <htmlurl url="mailto:x@example.com" name="x@example.com"> (auto-linked email)
Percent: 50%
Backslash: \\

